A great find!

On 17/07/2019 you visited Norfolk Park, Sheffield and it was your highest DECIDE recording priority visit this month. On this visit you recorded 3 species. Our pick from these species is Holly Blue. In total, 35 records of this species were made this month by online recorders such as yourself.
